   <body>
      <prereq>During the relay test the relay switches to its active state.
Before starting make sure that it is approved to perform the test,
especially if the active relay signal triggers a remote action.</prereq>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p id="MakeSureYouAreLoggedInAsAUserWithSe-B16DDBF2">Make
sure you are logged in as a user with <uicontrol translate="no">Service</uicontrol> access. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Press the <uicontrol>Main menu icon</uicontrol> and navigate
to <uicontrol translate="no">Service &gt; General &gt; Relaytest</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Press on the <uicontrol translate="no">Start</uicontrol> button for the relay you want to test.</p>
            <p>
               <note>For more information about the relays refer to the <i>Drawings</i>.</note>
               <fig>
                  <image href="../Images/PRIME_Relaytest_DD00610412.png" placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
